-- Roesler Opposes Increase in Euro Bailout Funds, Passauer Says
-- B y   B r i a n   P a r k i n
-- 2012-03-07T07:14:44Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-07/roesler-opposes-increase-in-euro-bailout-funds-passauer-says.html
German Economy Minister Philipp Roesler opposes international calls to make  Europe ’s permanent
rescue fund bigger, the  Passaer Neue Presse  newspaper reported,
citing an interview.  There is “currently no need” to boost the European
Stability Mechanism, Roesler was cited as saying.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Brian Parkin in Berlin at 
